# Backend API

- Database: Supabase
- Vector Store: Supabase
- Auth: Supabase
- Storage: Supabase
- LLM Model API: OpenRouter

## Backend Overview

The backend provides two main APIs:
1. User Authentication (handled by Supabase)
2. Streaming LLM chat completions
3. Storing chat history for users
4. Uploading files to our storage which are then converted to vector embeddings stored in our database


